            'description' => '{"en":"<p>Support Center - Your Partner in Academic Assistance<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Welcome to our Support Center at Tutor Hub. We understand that academic matters can be challenging, and we are dedicated to providing you with the assistance and guidance you need. Whether you&#39;re a patient seeking support or a visitor with questions, we&#39;re here to assist you.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Patient Support: If you are a current patient, our support team is committed to addressing your queries and concerns. Reach out to us via the contact information provided in your patient account, or utilize our patient portal for secure communication.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>General Inquiries: For general inquiries or if you&#39;re considering our doctoring services, our support team can provide initial information and guide you through the process. Contact us through the form on this page, and we&#39;ll ensure your inquiry is directed to the appropriate department.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Technical Support: Facing technical difficulties with our website or patient portal? Our technical support team is available to help you. Please provide specific details about the issue you&#39;re encountering, and we&#39;ll work swiftly to resolve it.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Contact Information:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Phone: [Your Tutor Hub Phone Number]<br \\/>\\r\\nEmail: [Your Support Email Address]<br \\/>\\r\\nOffice Hours: [Your Operating Hours]<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs):<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Visit our FAQs page for answers to common questions. This resource is regularly updated to offer quick solutions to any queries you may have.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Submit a Support Request<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Use the form below to submit a support request. Please provide detailed information about your inquiry, and our team will promptly respond to assist you.<\\/p>","hi":"<p>\\u0938\\u0939\\u093e\\u092f\\u0924\\u093e \\u0915\\u0947\\u0902\\u0926\\u094d\\u0930 - \\u